.admin-actions.my-3
  %header.admin-actions__head
    %span.admin-actions__title
      %i.fa-solid.fa-screwdriver-wrench{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      Administration
    %span.admin-actions__subtitle
      %i.fa-solid.fa-lock{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      Admin-only

  %p.admin-actions__lede
    Repository-structure operations. These actions change how objects are arranged and surfaced across the repository, so they apply repository-wide and live behind the admin gate.

  .admin-actions__grid{role: 'list'}
    = link_to admin_reparent_path, class: 'admin-action-card admin-action-card--structure', role: 'listitem' do
      %span.admin-action-card__icon
        %i.fa-solid.fa-sitemap{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      %span.admin-action-card__title Re-parent / Move
      %span.admin-action-card__desc
        Move a Collection or Community to a new parent. Re-orders the structural tree and re-flows every descendant's breadcrumb and contents.
      %span.admin-action-card__cta
        Open
        %i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-right-long{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}

    = link_to admin_linked_members_path, class: 'admin-action-card admin-action-card--link', role: 'listitem' do
      %span.admin-action-card__icon
        %i.fa-solid.fa-link{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      %span.admin-action-card__title Linked members
      %span.admin-action-card__desc
        Surface a single Work in additional Collections without duplicating it. Adds discovery placement only — it never changes the Work's permissions.
      %span.admin-action-card__cta
        Open
        %i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-right-long{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}

    = link_to admin_people_path, class: 'admin-action-card admin-action-card--people', role: 'listitem' do
      %span.admin-action-card__icon
        %i.fa-solid.fa-users{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      %span.admin-action-card__title Manage people
      %span.admin-action-card__desc
        Create Person records by NUID, curate the authoritative display name / title / bio / ORCID, and manage the community affiliations that drive the Faculty & Staff browse.
      %span.admin-action-card__cta
        Open
        %i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-right-long{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}

    = link_to admin_impersonation_path, class: 'admin-action-card admin-action-card--impersonation', role: 'listitem' do
      %span.admin-action-card__icon
        %i.fa-solid.fa-user-secret{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
      %span.admin-action-card__title Impersonation
      %span.admin-action-card__desc
        Act as another user (writes attributed to them) or view the repository read-only as they see it. A persistent banner marks the session.
      %span.admin-action-card__cta
        Open
        %i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-right-long{'aria-hidden' => 'true'}
